rows.label: qst300305_msg001
rows.name: After interview 1 FEV

rows.label: qst300305_msg002
rows.name:
If you think they're a spy,
choose black. If they're
innocent, choose white.

rows.label: qst300305_msg003
rows.name: Black

rows.label: qst300305_msg004
rows.name: White

rows.label: qst300305_msg005
rows.name: I see, that's how you feel.

rows.label: qst300305_msg006
rows.name:
I think it's questionable
whether they're even Gulan.

rows.label: qst300305_msg007
rows.name: All right, let's move on.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0001
rows.name: Um...[ML:Dash ] Nice to meet you, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0002
rows.name: I'm Powapowa from Avaritia, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0003
rows.name:
I came here because I wanted
a non-combat job, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0004
rows.name: I'll be asking you some questions.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0005
rows.name: Yes, sir!

rows.label: qst300305_msg0051
rows.name: What should I ask?

rows.label: qst300305_msg0052
rows.name: Motivation

rows.label: qst300305_msg0053
rows.name: Skills

rows.label: qst300305_msg0054
rows.name: Future goals

rows.label: qst300305_msg0055
rows.name: Nothing in particular

rows.label: qst300305_msg0101
rows.name:
I wanted to work for a Merc
Group, but it was all fighting,
so I was in a bind, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0102
rows.name:
I heard you needed someone to
help out here, so I came, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0103
rows.name:
Why do you want to work
for a Merc Group?

rows.label: qst300305_msg0104
rows.name:
Um, you see, Powapowa...
I like big people, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0105
rows.name:
I was hoping a big mercenary
would pet me, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0201
rows.name: Um... As for what I'm good at...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst300305_msg0202
rows.name:
Powapowa's pride is this fur! It's
fluffy and soft to the touch, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0203
rows.name: Don't you mind if everyone touches you?

rows.label: qst300305_msg0204
rows.name:
Everyone says that petting Powapowa
brings them happiness, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0205
rows.name:
I want to soothe the battle-weary
mercenaries with Powapowa's
fluffiness, so I welcome it, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0301
rows.name: I don't have any grand goals, but...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst300305_msg0302
rows.name:
I want sad and lonely people to
pet Powapowa and be happy, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0303
rows.name:
Isn't it hard to maintain
your fluffiness?

rows.label: qst300305_msg0304
rows.name:
It is, mo. Daily
grooming is a must, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0305
rows.name:
That's why this village, with
its clean water for bathing,
is perfect for Powapowa, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0401
rows.name: This concludes the interview.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0402
rows.name:
We will inform you of the
results later. You may go.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0403
rows.name:
I understand, mo. I'll be
waiting for good news, mo.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0404
rows.name: Now, I'll call the next candidate.

rows.label: qst300305_msg0501
rows.name:
Is there anything else
you'd like to ask?
